faqs.question: What is Jarvis?
faqs.answer: Jarvis is an AI-powered trading assistant for Solana tokens.

faqs.question: How do I start trading?
faqs.answer: Use `/balance` to check your wallet, then `/buy <token> <amount>` to make a trade.

faqs.question: What are the fees?
faqs.answer: There are no fees for using Jarvis. You only pay standard Solana network fees.

faqs.question: How do I contact support?
faqs.answer: Contact @matthaynes88 on Telegram or use the `/help` command.

faqs.question: Is my wallet safe?
faqs.answer: Yes, Jarvis never stores your private keys. All transactions require your approval.
